name: Corporal Beezer
Lore: 'Alderaanian slicer and technician. Trained by Brooks Carlson to serve as a Scout for Alliance commandos. She gets nervous when General Solo tries to hotwire something.',
Text: 'Prevents opponent from ''reacting'' to same site. Once during each of your deploy phases, may deploy one device to same location from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Rebels of ability < 3 and [Endor] Rebels are immune to Scanning Crew.',
